'''國際年齡分級聯盟'''（{{lang-en|International Age Rating Coalition}}，縮寫'''IARC'''）是一個旨在簡化電子遊戲在不同國家獲得[[內容評級|內容評級]]流程的機構。於2013年開始，IARC系統簡化了評級過程，開發人員可以通過回答問卷來得到產品內容分級。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.globalratings.com/about.aspx |title=About the International Age Rating Coalition {{!}} IARC<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-11-02 |archive-date=2020-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214195848/https://www.globalratings.com/about.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kotaku.com.au/2014/03/the-government-is-in-the-process-of-changing-how-we-classify-games/ |title=The Government Is In The Process Of Changing How We Classify Games {{!}} Kotaku Australia<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-11-02 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111165754/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2014/03/the-government-is-in-the-process-of-changing-how-we-classify-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在線上獲得產品的評級的過程中降低遊戲開發商的成本。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://games.on.net/2014/03/the-iarc-explained-and-why-you-should-care/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419144942/http://games.on.net/2014/03/the-iarc-explained-and-why-you-should-care/ |archive-date=2014-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

這項成果是來自世界各地的評級機構一起建立的，包括北美的[[娛樂軟件分級委員會|娛樂軟件分級委員會]]，歐洲的[[泛歐遊戲資訊組織|泛歐遊戲資訊組織]]，德國的[[德國娛樂軟件檢驗局|USK]]，巴西的ClassInd和澳洲的[[澳大利亚分级委员会|ACB]]，並且首次在2013年倫敦遊戲會議上宣布。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dealspwn.com/international-age-ratings-system-160904 |title=New International Age Ratings System Launching Worldwide Next Year {{!}} Video Game Deals & UK News {{!}} Dealspwn.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2016-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322134006/http://www.dealspwn.com/international-age-ratings-system-160904 |archive-date=2016-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2014年8月，澳大利亚分级委员会提出修訂，允許採用IARC的自動評級。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2014/09/01/getting-digitally-distributed-games-classified-in-australia-to-be-cost-free |title=Getting Digitally-Distributed Games Classified in Australia to Be Cost-Free - IGN<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-11-02 |archive-date=2014-09-01 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140901180920/http://au.ign.com/articles/2014/09/01/getting-digitally-distributed-games-classified-in-australia-to-be-cost-free |dead-url=no }}</ref>

